<subSubSection id="C3574FB843E20478B43844DA6F585B69" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="D601B4171ED30ED29BABA2D3E680AD70" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Material examined.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1A931F06FF2AD29141840C4E5D50D978" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
SRI LANKA, on inflorescence of bamboo, January 1855, G.H.K. Thwaites s.n. (ex herb. M.J. Berkeley), K(M)52469, 
<emphasis id="2AEC04174C5B9A07B64E4385C0F4416E" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">isotype</emphasis>
